      </div>
    
      <div class="gallery-cell">
        <div class="quote">
            <div class="text-container">
                <img src="webpage/bg-pattern-quotation.svg" class="quote-1" />
                Pasar de expedientes en papel a digital realmente me ahorra tiempo, en especial enviar las recetas por email con mi firma digital en automático
                <div class="client">Alejandra Morales - Ginecóloga</div>
                <img src="webpage/bg-pattern-quotation2.svg" class="quote-2"  />
            </div>
        </div>
       </div>
    </div>
</div>
<style>
* {
  -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.container-quotes{
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
}
.title-quotes{
    color: #fff;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0em;
    z-index: 10;
    margin: 0 auto;
    right: 0;
    left: 0;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    font-family: 'Rubik';
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 4.2rem;
    line-height: 2.8rem;
}
.gallery.js-flickity{
    background: #009BA9;
    padding-top: 8rem;
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
}
.client{
    color: #009BA9;
}
.quote{
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: nowrap;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    flex-direction: row;
    height: 100%;
}
.text-container{
    display: flex;
    flex-flow: column;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex-wrap: nowrap;
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 7px;
    height: 80%;
    width: 80%;
    background-color: azure;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 5em;
    gap: 1.5em;
    font-size: 1.25em;
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
}
.quote-1{
    position: absolute;
    top: 1em;
    left: 1em;
    width: 25px;
}
.quote-2{
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1em;
    right: 1em;
    width: 25px;
}

.gallery {
  background: #EEE;
}

.gallery-cell {
  width: 66%;
  height: 200px;
  margin-right: 10px;
  /* background: #8C8; */
  counter-increment: gallery-cell;
}

/* cell number */
.gallery-cell:before {
  display: block;
  text-align: center;
  /* content: counter(gallery-cell); */
  line-height: 200px;
  font-size: 80px;
  color: white;
}

@media only screen and (min-width: 300px) and (max-width: 700px) {
    .text-container {
        padding: 10px;
        padding-top: 25px;
        font-size: 0.85em;
        line-height: 1.5;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .quote-1,
    .quote-2{
        width: 15px;
    }
    .gallery{
        padding-top: 10rem;
    }
    h1.title-quotes{
        padding-top: 0.5em;
        line-height: 3.8rem;
        font-size: 3.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>